name: What's Missing? (itch)
description:
What's Missing? Is a surreal puzzle game where you guess the differences between the repeating identical rooms. It first starts simple with a window or books, but soon you'll see that so much more things can change that you ever can imagine. Figure it out yourself!

Follow us on Twitter to see what we're currently working on!

What's Missing? (@Whats_Missing_) / Twitter
